<task id="006" project="sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix">
  <metadata>
    <title>Confirm CI guard size ceiling: baseline+10% default (UQ-05)</title>
    <status>completed</status>
    <estimated-effort>15 minutes</estimated-effort>
    <actual-effort>~5 min (design default applied; owner ACK via task 001)</actual-effort>
    <assigned>Project owner</assigned>
    <started>2026-05-24</started>
    <completed>2026-05-24</completed>
    <tags>coordination, phase-0, ci-cd</tags>
    <parallel-group>A</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Independent owner decision; no file conflicts</parallel-reason>
    <rigor>STANDARD</rigor>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Confirm the CI guard size ceiling to use in Phase 6 task 074 (`Deploy-BffApi.ps1`
    hard-fail size guard). Default per spec.md §Assumptions is baseline + 10%. Owner may tighten
    to baseline + 5% if confident, or set an absolute threshold.
  </prompt>

  <role>Project coordinator.</role>

  <goal>
    Specific numeric value documented for the CI guard threshold (percentage or absolute MB),
    to be used as input for Phase 6 task 070 / FR-C5 implementation.
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="design-spec">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/design.md</file>
    <file purpose="ai-spec">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/spec.md</file>
    <file purpose="constraint">.claude/constraints/azure-deployment.md</file>
    <file purpose="deploy-script">scripts/Deploy-BffApi.ps1</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec.md FR-C5">Hard-fails if publish zip exceeds documented ceiling unless `-AllowOversize` flag is passed</constraint>
    <constraint source="design.md §3">Default: baseline + 10%; owner can tighten</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/constraints/azure-deployment.md</file>
      <file>scripts/Deploy-BffApi.ps1</file>
      <file>projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/spec.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>
      Baseline (~60 MB per constraint doc) + 10% = ~66 MB ceiling. Tighter (+5%) = ~63 MB. The
      ceiling becomes the hard-fail threshold for `Deploy-BffApi.ps1` in Phase 6, plus the CI
      step that fails on oversized publish.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="001" status="not-started">Owner sign-off required first</dependency>
    </dependencies>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Owner reviews current baseline (~60 MB) and design.md §3 default</step>
    <step order="2">Owner picks percentage (+5% or +10%) or absolute number</step>
    <step order="3">Record numeric ceiling in CLAUDE.md Decisions Made</step>
    <step order="4">Phase 0 checklist item — no specific item for UQ-05 in design §6 Phase 0; record in CLAUDE.md only</step>
    <step order="5">Update TASK-INDEX.md status of task 006 from 🔲 to ✅</step>
  </steps>

  <tools><tool name="git">Update CLAUDE.md</tool></tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="docs">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/CLAUDE.md (Decisions Made entry with numeric ceiling)</output>
    <output type="docs">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md (status update)</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">Numeric size ceiling (percentage or MB) recorded in CLAUDE.md</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Value is consumable by Phase 6 task 070 implementation</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    <completion-summary>
      UQ-05 = baseline + 10% (design.md §3 default applied; owner ACK via task 001 covers this). Current
      pre-Outcome-A baseline is ~75.2 MB compressed (per 2026-05-24 smoke-test deploy). If Phase 3 baseline
      after Outcome A SAFE candidates is ~60 MB, ceiling = ~66 MB. Phase 3 task 035 captures the
      authoritative baseline; Phase 6 task 070 consumes the +10% formula in Deploy-BffApi.ps1 hard-fail
      guard + CI step (FR-C5). Owner reserves right to tighten to +5% after Outcome A measurable results.
    </completion-summary>
    <ceiling-formula>baseline + 10%</ceiling-formula>
    <baseline-source>Phase 3 task 035 (compressed publish.zip size)</baseline-source>
    <consumed-by>Phase 6 task 070 (Deploy-BffApi.ps1 hard-fail size guard); CI gate per FR-C5</consumed-by>
  </notes>
</task>
